Package: conservR
Title: Calculate Residue Conservation Scores from Multiple Sequence Alignments
Description: Current version of the package conatins 4 functions to perform multiple sequence alignments of
    protein sequences, calculate residue conservation scores using the
    BLOSUM62 substitution matrix, and visualize conservation patterns as
    heatmaps and lineplot. The package is designed for rapid
    protein conservation analysis and generation of publication-quality
    figures.
Version: 1.0.0
